  <name>Frigate Config GUI</name>
  <summary>GUI tool for configuring Frigate NVR</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A user-friendly graphical interface for creating and editing Frigate NVR configuration files.
      Simplifies the process of setting up cameras, detection parameters, and other Frigate features
      without manually editing YAML files.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Easy camera configuration</li>
      <li>Semantic search setup</li>
      <li>Real-time validation</li>
      <li>Import/export configuration files</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <categories>
    <category>Utility</category>
    <category>Settings</category>
  </categories>
